# Uploads — `uploads/` is left unanchored so backend/uploads/* (the
# real runtime upload path for profile photos, vault, wordlists)
# stays ignored. `evidence/` is anchored to repo root because the
# unanchored form was accidentally swallowing
# frontend/src/app/engagements/[id]/evidence/ — a Next.js route
# whose /[eid]/page.tsx never got committed and 404'd on every
# fresh deploy. Runtime evidence goes to MinIO, not disk; the
# root-anchored ignore is kept only in case someone flips storage
# back to local at the repo root.
uploads/
/evidence/

